text: Jordan Bos (born 29 October 2002) is an Australian soccer player. He plays for Westerlo in the Belgian Pro League and for the Australia men's national soccer team. ==Honours== Melbourne City *A-League Premiership: 2021–22, 2022–23 ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:Soccer players from Melbourne
